import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; import axios from "../api/axios"; import apiRoute from "../api/apiRoute"; function ClientProfile() { const { id } = useParams(); const [userData, setUserData] = useState([]); const [userDataBookings, setUserDataBookings] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { async function fetchData() { try { const dataResponse = await axios.get(apiRoute.clients + `/${id}`); setUserData(dataResponse.data); const dataResponse2 = await axios.get( apiRoute.bookings + `/history/${id}` ); setUserDataBookings(dataResponse2.data); } catch (error) { console.log(error); // error message notification } } fetchData(); }, [id]); console.log(userData); console.log(userDataBookings); return (
